  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Leone.jpg",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 15th level your mind and body are the embodiment of the lion, forever engaged with hunt. Choose a physical contidtion that isn't Stunned, Prone Restrained or Grappled. You gain immunity to that condtition, this can not be changed later. Also if you would lose a limb excluding your head while you are <strong>Beastlike Appearance</strong>, you regain it at the start of your next turn. This becomes 1 minute when you are not transformed.</p><p>At 18th level, whenever you would fail your last death saving throw or be instantly killed you instead ignore it and immediately gain hit points up to half your maximum. This ability activates once per long rest.</p>",
